OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FEngland and Scotland have gained their
OL,7,Ffirst gold medals at the Commonwealth
OL,8,FGames as the competition gets underway
OL,9,Fin Glasgow.
OL,11,FScotland's Duncan Scott spoke of his
OL,12,F"relief" after delighting the home
OL,13,Fcrowd at Tollcross International
OL,14,FSwimming Centre by winning gold in the
OL,15,Fmen's 200m individual medley.
OL,17,FThe 29-year-old, an eight-time Olympic
OL,18,Fmedallist, set a Commonwealth Games
OL,19,Frecord of one minute 56.28 seconds
OL,20,Fafter taking the lead on the
OL,21,Fbackstroke leg of the race.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
