OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784933304
OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FScott said: "I just wanted to try and
OL,7,Ftake it out, a really good backstroke
OL,8,Fsplit in there and good learning.
OL,10,F"So I guess from the swimming side,
OL,11,Fthat was the focus, but also from a
OL,12,Fmore emotional standpoint and from the
OL,13,Fteam, it was like, try and get the
OL,14,Fmomentum going and a bit of a weight
OL,15,Fon the shoulders for that.
OL,17,F"But I'm glad and (it's) more of a
OL,18,Frelief rather than anything else.
OL,26,@nD@MOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784933304
OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,F"The swim team this morning did a
OL,7,Fgreat job. Obviously, the final
OL,8,Fsession tonight has just begun, so
OL,9,Fhopefully (there are) plenty more
OL,10,Fmedals to come."
OL,12,FScotland's Faye Rogers also pleased
OL,13,Fthe home crowd by winning gold in the
OL,14,Fwomen's 200m individual medley SM10
OL,15,Ffinal, with her medal ceremony
OL,16,Freceiving a huge ovation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]
