OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FParalympic swimmer Stephen Clegg
OL,7,Fclaimed silver in the men's S13 100m
OL,8,Ffreestyle, while fellow Scot Katie
OL,9,FShanahan took silver in the women's
OL,10,F200m backstroke.
OL,12,FMark Swan won England's first gold
OL,13,Fmedal of the Games with a dramatic
OL,14,Fvictory in the men's lightweight
OL,15,Fcategory of the men's para
OL,16,Fpowerlifting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
