CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784933304
OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FSwan admitted he thought he had come
OL,7,Fup short after failing with his final
OL,8,Flift ` but he in fact topped the
OL,9,Fstandings over Nigeria's Roland
OL,10,FEzuruike by the slimmest of margins,
OL,11,Fbased on a co-efficient related to
OL,12,Fbody weight.
OL,14,FSwan lifted 222kg, more than three
OL,15,Ftimes his body weight, with his second
OL,16,Flift.
OL,18,FHe said: "I came back off the third
OL,19,Flift and thought, 'Well, I've got
OL,20,Fbronze'. My coach said 'good job on
OL,21,Fgold'. I thought he was winding me up."
OL,26,@zD@JOU}D@gO]
