OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FEngland team-mate Olivia Broome
OL,7,Fclaimed a bronze medal in the women's
OL,8,Flightweight category to add to the
OL,9,Fsilver medal she secured at the 2022
OL,10,FGames in Birmingham.
OL,12,FSilver medals were also gained by
OL,13,FEngland's Matthew Harding in the men's
OL,14,Fheavyweight para powerlifting, and
OL,15,FGabriel Langton, Joshua Nathan, Adam
OL,16,FTobin, Luke Whitehouse, Alexander
OL,17,FYolshin-Cash in the artistic
OL,18,Fgymnastics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
