OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784933304
OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FEva Okaro, Freya Colbert, Leah
OL,7,FSchlosshan and Freya Anderson also
OL,8,Ftook silver in the women's 4x100m
OL,9,Ffreestyle relay, finishing behind a
OL,10,Fdominant Australian team.
OL,12,FJacob Mills, James Guy, Gabriel
OL,13,FShepherd, Jacob Whittle added another
OL,14,Fsilver in the men's 4x100m freestyle
OL,15,Frelay, with Australia setting a
OL,16,FCommonwealth Games record of 3:09.49.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
