OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784933304
OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FEngland's triple Olympic gold
OL,7,Fmedallist Tom Dean claimed bronze in
OL,8,Fthe men's 200m individual medley and
OL,9,Fthree-time Paralympian Matthew Redfern
OL,10,Fsecured a bronze in the men's 100m
OL,11,Ffreestyle S13.
OL,13,FTeen para swimmer Ela Letton-Jones
OL,14,Fgained Team Wales' first medal with a
OL,15,Fsilver-winning swim.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
