OL,3,CEngland and Scotland win first gold
OL,4,Cmedals at Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FAdam Peaty, the three-time Olympic
OL,7,Fgold medallist, won the men's 100m
OL,8,Fbreaststroke semi-final in a time of
OL,9,F59.19 seconds and fellow Englishman
OL,10,FGregory Butler also qualified for the
OL,11,Ffinal after finishing third in 1:00.12.
